axis2.name: # #{PRAutoConversion}
axis2.text:
SUM(
CASE WHEN "EKKO"."STATU" = 'B'
THEN 1.0
ELSE 0.0
END
)

variables.name: rework_activities
variables.value: 'Adjustment Charge','Block Purchase Order Item','Cancel Goods Receipt','Cancel Invoice Receipt','Change Currency','Change Price','Change Quantity','Change Vendor','Delete Purchase Order Item','Dun Order Confirmation','Reactivate Purchase Order Item','Send Overdue Notice','Send Purchase Order Update'

variables.name: filter6
variables.value:
CASE
    WHEN ISNULL("LFA1"."VBUND") = 1 THEN 'External'
    ELSE 'Internal'
END

variables.name: filter7
variables.value:
CASE WHEN ISNULL("EKPO"."LOEKZ") = 1 THEN 'not deleted'
     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'S' THEN 'locked'
     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'L' THEN 'deleted'
     ELSE "EKPO"."LOEKZ"
END

axis2.name: #{AutomaticConversion} #{ThroughputTime} #{ShortPR} - #{ShortPO}
axis2.text:
AVG(CASE
WHEN "EKKO"."STATU" = 'B' 
THEN CALC_THROUGHPUT(ALL_OCCURRENCE['Process Start'] TO ALL_OCCURRENCE['Process End'], REMAP_TIMESTAMPS("_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", DAYS))
ELSE NULL 
END
)
axis2.translatedName: Automatic Conversion Throughput Time PR - PO

axis2.name: #{Non}#{AutomaticConversion} #{ThroughputTime} #{ShortPR} - #{ShortPO}
axis2.text:
AVG(CASE
WHEN "EKKO"."STATU" != 'B' 
THEN CALC_THROUGHPUT(ALL_OCCURRENCE['Process Start'] TO ALL_OCCURRENCE['Process End'], REMAP_TIMESTAMPS("_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", DAYS))
ELSE NULL 
END
)
axis2.translatedName: Non-Automatic Conversion Throughput Time PR - PO
